{"tid":539022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港可以咁on9 到到都天橋連天橋","createTime":"2018-01-24T07:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T17:29:38.000Z","uid":137729,"like":21,"dislike":258,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"b3be4c4625f840b67d48a07321f8dd06fd62a330","tid":539022,"uid":137729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/153507_b56491141e397721134d5ea58609125e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F153507_b56491141e397721134d5ea58609125e.jpeg&h=98b9471a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港發展有時真係好on9<br />\n台北有d地方同香港好似都係商廈林立<br />\n但有d地方個種新舊交替 兩種感覺同時存在好舒服<br />\n太陽曬落大雨時係街到行係會唔方便<br />\n但起碼可以感受到當地人生活<br />\n<br />\n睇返香港 新發展既都會有天橋<br />\n商場連商場 屋苑連屋苑<br />\n明明唔同區 但環境都係差唔多 都係連鎖店連鎖店連鎖店<br />\n所有野都係copy&amp;paste 毫無新意<br />\n點解香港可以咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解人地做到 香港永遠都做咩到"},{"pid":"0ab6c73055f395f8761a4b347ef8305cffb84be1","tid":539022,"uid":107927,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"人口太多"},{"pid":"c2944bc1e4cdb70a2b07ca6aaa7f2ba28682e57d","tid":539022,"uid":151324,"like":194,"dislike":12,"score":182,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"就係你呢d人令到成個社會落後"},{"pid":"58cd348b2efd93467f350ca0c8da20b2fbd17170","tid":539022,"uid":3454,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n好出奇呀?"},{"pid":"0df899510d82e2540bd4e4e00b6ad043d6875214","tid":539022,"uid":137729,"like":2,"dislike":43,"score":-41,"quote":{"pid":"c2944bc1e4cdb70a2b07ca6aaa7f2ba28682e57d","tid":539022,"uid":151324,"like":194,"dislike":12,"score":182,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"就係你呢d人令到成個社會落後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"我都想有咁大影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid